posting_body: ['When you play as hard as you work, time is everything.', 'Franklin 299 Apartments in Redwood City is designed to let you focus on what’s important to you, whatever that may be.', 'Smartly designed living spaces and high-end finishes combine to create a relaxing space to suit your lifestyle here at our pet-friendly apartments in Redwood City, CA.', 'Franklin 299 hits the sweet spot: urban delights, transportation galore, and a warm home to call your own.', 'Adjacent to Downtown Redwood City, the community is a stone’s throw from restaurants, theaters, services, stores, highways, and just about everything else.', 'Come and explore our community and discover a new standard of living.', '-Patio/Balcony', '-Fitness Center', '-NEST Thermostats', '-Bike Storage', '-Pool', '-BBQ/Picnic Area', '-Concierge', '-Dry Cleaning Hub', '-Firepits', '-Business Center', '-Vaulted Ceilings', '-Open Floorplans', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'DRE# 1973501', 'Professionally Managed by Cushman & Wakefield', 'Equal Opportunity Housing Provider.']
